    %link{:rel => "shortcut icon", :href => "/favicon.png"}
    = haml :analytics
  %body
    %section#head
      %header
        %h1
          Lenvyx
        .tagline
          It's ubuntu Linux for your HP Envy
    %section#warning
      %p.warning
        The Lenvyx project has been abandonned by its creator – Sudeep Nayak – in 2012.<br />
        I (Adrien Jarthon) am still maintaining the website, twitter and scripts, but I do not have the skills nor time to improve lenvyx.<br />
        The project is totaly usable, it's just limited to the features below. Any help is appreciated (test, advices, pull requests, ...).
    %section#content
      #main= yield
